Colour:
Carapace and mesosoma brownish-green, slightly paler ventrally; dark pigmentation around median and lateral ocelli. Pedipalps and legs lighter, distal part of femur and proximal part of patella darker especially on legs III and IV. Pectines light yellow to cream. Metasoma brown to yellow, segments darker dorsally, segment 
V
darker than preceding segments. Telson vesicle yellowish-brown; aculeus brown anteriorly, becoming dark brown to black posteriorly. 
